com.stremebase.map

Class SetMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.stremebase.base.StremeMap
      • com.stremebase.base.DynamicMap
        • com.stremebase.map.SetMap

  • public class SetMap
extends DynamicMap
    SetMap associates a key with a set or a bag of values. Set the set type in constructor: SetMap.SET: An ordinary set SetMap.MULTISET: A bag - occurrences are counted SetMap.ATTRIBUTEDSET: Values can be further associated with an arbitrary tag (for example type or weight of value)

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  SetMap.SetEntry
      SetEntry contains not only key and value, but also an attribute for MULTISETs, the attribute is the count of values for ATTRIBUTEDSETs, you can assign any value but DB.NULL
